    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback expected of this chassis. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and longevity.",
